name: Static_shorterThanTest
description: Unit tests for the Static.shorterThan method, which checks if an Iterable or Collection is shorter than a given number.

test_cases.name: testShorterThan_Collection
test_cases.description: Tests the shorterThan method with a Collection, checking if it correctly identifies when the collection is shorter than a given number.

test_cases.name: testShorterThan_Iterable
test_cases.description: Tests the shorterThan method with an Iterable, checking if it correctly identifies when the iterable is shorter than a given number.

test_cases.name: testShorterThan_NonCollectionIterable
test_cases.description: Tests the shorterThan method with a non-Collection Iterable, checking if it correctly identifies when the iterable is shorter than a given number.

test_cases.name: testShorterThan_NonPositiveN
test_cases.description: Tests the shorterThan method with non-positive values for n, checking if it correctly handles such cases.
